---
title: Radish & Caramelised Pear Salad with Almonds & Parmesan | Serves 2
description: This delightful salad gets a pleasant burst of sweetness from the caramelised pear, crunch from roasted almonds and colour
from the radish. Toss it together with a sticky balsamic glaze, and you’ve got yourself a salad for the senses!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/caramelised-pear-and-radish-salad-098124b8.jpg
